<H3> <TI>   Supreme Council Lifts Conditions on Ratification </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0302200694 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1928 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0302200694 </F>
