<F P=106> [By UKRINFORM-TASS] </F>
  [Text] Kiev February 3 TASS -- The Ukrainian parliament 
lifted conditions attached earlier to the ratification of the 
START-1, accepting the Lisbon protocol appended to the treaty. 
  Thus the lawmakers approved President Leonid Kravchuk's 
signing of the tripartite accords during the Ukraine-Russia-U.S. 
summit in Moscow. 

