<F P=106> [From the "Diplomatic Panorama" feature] </F>
  [Text] A Russian delegation is due to leave for Kiev on 
February 8 to draw up, jointly with Ukrainian officials, a set 
of measures to implement the Russian-Ukrainian-U.S. agreements 
