<H3> <TI>   Supreme Council Approves Kravchuk's Resolution on START I </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0302180294 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1732 GMT 3 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0302180294 </F>
