  [Text] Havana, 21 Jan (PL) -- The Cuban Justice Ministry 
said today a delegation of the Argentine Secretariat for the 
Prevention of Drug Addiction and the Struggle Against Drug 
Trafficking is negotiating a cooperation agreement in that 
sphere with the Cuban National Drug Commission. 
  The Argentine delegation is led by Eduardo Luis Gonzalez, 
the 
