<F P=106> [Article by Ignacio Gutierrez A.] </F>
  [Text] Yesterday, the attorney general of the republic, 
Diego Valades Rios, made the first appointments of his 
administration, confirming Humberto Benitez Trevino as assistant 
attorney for preliminary investigations. He also designated 
Marcos Castillejos Escobar as assistant attorney for process 
control; Ricardo Franco Guzman, as assistant juridical attorney; 
and Alfonso Cabrera Morales, as assistant attorney for local 
offices and inspections. Javier Duenas Garcia was named chief 
