Patino, as head of the Planning Center for Drug Control. As of 
yesterday, Fernando Aguilar became the new director of news 
media for the federal institution of justice, and Javier 
Casillas Zabalza, the private secretary to the head of the PGR 
[Office of the Attorney General of the Republic]. 
  The new officials assumed their posts immediately, and were 
called upon by Diego Valades to "expend all their professional 
capacity and dedication to service on the critical tasks of the 
prosecution of justice, with strict adherence to the law and 
deep respect for human rights." 

